function autoStockOpsForOrder(o,data,rid,by='Auto Sale'){let recipes=rf(data.recipes||[],rid),items=rf(data.inventoryItems||[],rid),need={};(o.items||[]).forEach(mi=>{let rec=recipes.find(r=>r.menuItemId===mi.menuItemId);(rec?.ingredients||[]).forEach(ing=>{need[ing.itemId]=(need[ing.itemId]||0)+(+ing.qty||0)*(+mi.qty||1)})});let ops=[];Object.entries(need).forEach(([itemId,qty])=>{let it=items.find(i=>i.id===itemId);if(it){ops.push({key:'stockIssues',item:{id:uid('issue'),restaurantId:rid,itemId:it.id,itemName:it.name,qty,unit:it.unit,department:it.department,takenBy:'POS Sale',approvedBy:by,purpose:'Auto stock deduction from bill '+String(o.id).slice(-6),source:'Auto Sale',orderId:o.id,date:now(),createdAt:now()}});ops.push({key:'inventoryItems',item:{...it,currentStock:Math.max(0,(+it.currentStock||0)-qty)}})}});return ops}
function bookingCode(){let d=new Date(),dd=String(d.getDate()).padStart(2,'0'),mm=String(d.getMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0'),yyyy=d.getFullYear(),rnd=String(Math.floor(Math.random()*10000)).padStart(4,'0');return `BKG-${dd}${mm}${yyyy}-${rnd}`}
function renewalDate(r){return r.nextRenewalDate||r.renewalDate||r.trialEndsAt||r.createdAt||now()}
function remainingDays(r){return Math.max(0,Math.ceil((new Date(renewalDate(r))-new Date())/86400000))}
function planStatus(r){let ps=r.paymentStatus||'Trial';if(['Suspended','Expired'].includes(ps))return ps;if(new Date(renewalDate(r))<new Date())return 'Expired';if(ps==='Paid'||ps==='Renewed'||ps==='Continue Service')return 'Active';return 'Trial'}
